Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.97,0:23:36.30,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}ゴールは近い
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.67,0:23:39.44,EDJP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}あと少し走ろう
