Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.93,0:23:04.78,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}向陌生人撒娇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.78,0:23:06.29,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}伤害到别人
