Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.69,0:23:10.74,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}但是今天从现在开始
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.74,0:23:12.26,EDCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}永不止步
